Privacy Policy
Razuma ("we", "our", or "us"), as an individual developer, operates mobile applications (the "Services") available on Android and iOS platforms. Your privacy is critically important to us, and this Privacy Policy aims to clarify our practices concerning the collection, processing, and disclosure of your non-personal information when you use our Services.
By accessing or using our Services, you agree to the collection and use of your information in accordance with this Privacy Policy. If you disagree with any part of this Privacy Policy, you are advised not to use our Services.
1. Information We Collect
**We Do Not Collect Biometric Information**
This application does not collect, store, or process any biometric information, including but not limited to face data or fingerprint data.
Automatically Collected Information
Device information (model, OS version, language settings, etc.)
Advertising ID (IDFA/AAID)
App usage statistics
IP address
Location data (approximate location)
Information Collected by Firebase Analytics
App usage statistics
Crash reports
User behavior data
Performance data
Information Collected by Admob
Ad display information
Ad interaction data
Information necessary for ad personalization
2. How We Use Your Information
Providing and improving app functionality
Optimizing ad delivery
Enhancing service quality
Resolving technical issues
Providing user support
3. Information Sharing
We may share information with third parties in the following cases:
Google LLC (for Firebase and Admob services)
When required by law
With user consent
4. Data Security
We implement appropriate security measures to protect the collected information.
5. Your Rights
Right to request access to their personal information
Right to request correction or deletion of their data
Right to request restriction of processing
Right to modify ad personalization settings
6. Children's Privacy
We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13 years of age.
7. Changes to This Policy
This policy may be updated without prior notice. Changes will be notified within the app.
